WEBVTT

00:00.896 --> 00:02.996
Previously on <i>Smash</i>.

00:05.252 --> 00:07.344
You're waiting to much time
to be in the ensemble.

00:07.345 --> 00:09.014
What, this brilliant director
is that powerful?

00:09.065 --> 00:11.233
You couldn't even say,
"sorry, I need a minute"?

00:11.267 --> 00:12.851
They're looking at someone
else for press secretary.

00:12.885 --> 00:15.637
Do they have you
in a little blonde wig

00:15.655 --> 00:17.389
- and a skirt that blows up?
- Okay...

00:17.423 --> 00:18.824
We haven't met yet.
I'm Tom.

00:18.858 --> 00:20.659
- I'm Sam.
- You slept with my wife.

00:20.693 --> 00:23.478
I made a terrible mistake.
Please don't go!

00:23.496 --> 00:24.913
How's <i>Marilyn</i> doing?

00:24.947 --> 00:26.681
She's having
some growing pains.

00:26.716 --> 00:29.251
If we land Rebecca Duvall,
I want a co-producer credit.

00:29.285 --> 00:32.170
Chasing after movie stars,
it's so lame.

00:32.220 --> 00:34.956
- Why can't the song be the star?
- Why can't I be the star?

00:35.864 --> 00:37.964
SMASH
S01 Ep10 - Understudy

00:38.432 --> 00:41.932
Sync and corrected by dr.jackson
for www.addic7ed.com

